text: Friedrich Fetz (2 November 1927 - 25 October 2013) was an Austrian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:2013 deaths Category:Austrian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Feldkirch District Category:Sportspeople from Vorarlberg
